high_descs: Turn left and walk toward the wall on the other side of the room.  Turn right and walk to the other side of  the room.  Turn right and walk toward the fireplace.  At the fireplace, turn right and walk to the coffee table.
Pick up the phone on the coffee table.
Walk toward the fireplace, turn left and walk around the coffee table.
Put the phone on the tray on the coffee table.
Pick up the tray with the phone from the coffee table.
Walk around the coffee table, toward the fireplace, turn right until on the opposite side of the coffee table
Put the tray with the phone down on the end table of the couch.
anns.task_desc: Drop phone in a tray and put on end table.

high_descs: Go around the left side of the couch, head over to the other side of the coffee table, facing the statue.
Pick up the phone on the coffee table.
Bring the phone around to the other side of the coffee table, facing the plate.
Put the phone on the plate on the table.
Pick up the plate with phone on the table.
Bring the plate around to the other side of the coffee table, to the small table left of the couch.
Put the plate with phone on the small table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a phone on it, on the table next to the couch.

high_descs: Walk to the other side of the couch by going around it in front of you to the left then walk to the coffee table in front of the couch.
Pick up the phone that's on the coffee table.
Walk to the other side of the coffee table.
Put the phone on the black plate that's on the coffee table.
Pick up the black plate.
Now walk to the end table to the left of the white couch.
Put the plate on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a phone on it on the end table.
